ide megacities. | Bloomberg\n\nBloomberg\n\nSHARE\n\nTwitter Facebook LinkedIn Email Print\n\nApr 23, 2024\n\nZhao Xiaowei did what would have been unthinkable just a few years ago: He\nquit his Beijing barista job and returned to his northeastern rust-belt\nhometown for a better future.\n\nTired of struggling to eke out a living in the nation\u2019s overpriced capital,\nthe 25-year-old is now earning more money running his own boutique cafe,\nserving up drip coffee made with high-grade Geisha beans for 60 yuan ($8.30) a\ncup.\n\n\"I\u2019m close to my family and there\u2019s a hot meal for me when I get home,\u201d Zhao\nsaid after making the move back to Dandong last June. \"And, most importantly,\nI have my own business.\u201d\n\nIn a time of both misinformation and too much information, quality journalism\nis more crucial than ever. By subscribing, you can help us get the story\nright.\n\nSUBSCRIBE NOW\n\n'Sugar Baby Riri' gets nine-year prison term over romance scam\n\nSponsored LinksSponsored Links\n\nPromoted LinksPromoted Links\n\nNo link to Nankai Trough quake seen after temblor in Shikoku\n\nSponsored LinksSponsored Links\n\nPromoted LinksPromoted Links\n\nTokyo host club worker arrested after underage girl racks up \u00a56 million in\ncharges\n\nSponsored LinksSponsored Links\n\nPromoted LinksPromoted Links\n\nPro Verbraucher\n\nVor 1988 geboren? Kassenpatienten haben Anspruch auf kostenlosen ZahnersatzPro\nVerbraucher\n\nSponsored bySponsored by\n\nCheckfox\n\nSolar-F\u00f6rder-Hammer in Sachsen: Deshalb m\u00fcssen Hausbesitzer schnell seinWie\nHausbesitzer von den neuen Ma\u00dfnahmen profitieren k\u00f6nnten.Checkfox\n\nSponsored bySponsored by\n\nKnauermann\n\nDas m\u00fcssen Sie wissen, bevor Sie eine hochwertige Smartwatch kaufenKnauermann\n\nSponsored bySponsored by\n\nSUBSCRIBE\n\n##### In your social network\n\nStay up to date with us on your social media platform of choice.\n\n##### In your inbox\n\nGet updates, insights and more via our newsle